id: pm-n28v
title: "CI: cache .agents/pm/search/lancedb + sentry release cache"
description: Tests and reindex flows generate a lancedb cache (~50MB) and sentry sourcemap upload caches. Caching them between runs avoids cold rebuild every time. Use actions/cache@v5 with restore-keys fallback. Skip cache invalidation when only docs change.
type: Issue
status: open
priority: 3
tags[4]: cache,ci,performance,pm-cli
created_at: "2026-05-16T22:07:59.834Z"
updated_at: "2026-05-16T22:07:59.834Z"
author: maintainer-agent
acceptance_criteria: lancedb cache restored on warm runs; sentry release cache restored when present; cache keys deterministic; no test runs against stale cache.
